  "heading_path": "GPT/Codex 中文风格深度语料报告 / 11. LaTex 成稿语料补充分析 / 11.5 最显著的风格切换：从代理自述到无主语教学",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 15,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00480:bf68155d09cd]]\n对话语料里，[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00481:380f832a2f8b]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00482:c14a41645f9b]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00483:bcbdd7aabcbf]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00484:15a1214b9c65]] 是明显的代理标记。CET-6 成稿中，这些表达全部为零：\n\n| 表达 | 策略报告 | [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00485:910eaeb58c6f]] | [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00486:85b859714d63]] | [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00487:2c16c190ae0d]] |\n|---|---:|---:|---:|---:|\n| [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00488:380f832a2f8b]] | 0 | 0 | 0 | 0 |\n| [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00489:c14a41645f9b]] | 0 | 0 | 0 | 0 |\n| [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00490:bcbdd7aabcbf]] | 0 | 0 | 0 | 0 |\n| [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00491:15a1214b9c65]] | 0 | 0 | 0 | 0 |\n\n替代它们的是无主语或读者导向的指令句：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00492:8cdc2d104edd]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00493:a62552381935]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00494:05bbc5793777]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00495:750fb31e5561]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00496:280f276a9754]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00497:93fb4298c27b]]。这使语言从[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00498:ec602fc05098]]变成[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00499:5d791356418f]]。\n\n这也是 GPT 面对长篇交付时最明显的成熟化：把过程叙述藏起来，把可复用的方法和结论放到前台。不过，读者如果需要知道推导过程，仍会发现许多段落保留了模型式的解释性铺垫。\n\n",
